<section  class="section section__call-to-action theme-purple block-align-center tight" >
  <div class="section__container">

    
          <h2 class="section__title default">
        What is Zelle?
      </h2>
    
          <div class="section__body default">
        <p>Zelle is a fast, safe and easy way to send and receive money directly between almost any bank accounts in the U.S., typically within minutes.<sup>1</sup>&nbsp; With just an email address or U.S. mobile phone number, you can send money to and receive money from friends, family and others you trust.</p>

      </div>
    
          <div class="section__actions">
                                                                              
                                    <a class="section__actions__cta  none-only" target=_blank rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://www.zellepay.com/" >Learn More</a>
                      
              </div>
    

  </div>
</section>
</div>
